messageBody:
--- In junit@yahoogroups.com, "Bob Runstein" <rrunstein@...> wrote:
>
> My company is interested in this product and I have viewed the demos
> on their site, but I'm not having much luck getting a callback from
> their sales department and only get voicemail at their office number
> 650-694-3000. We would like to get a demo copy or in house
> demonstration to see if it suits our need. If anyone from Agitar
> reads this, please call me at 720-744-5911. If anyone has any info on
> why they are so difficult to get ahold of, please let me know. Thanks.
>
> Bob Runstein
>

Hi Bob,

I am sorry nobody has gotten back to you. We've been very busy since
we've introduced AgitarOne last month and we are playing catch-up.
I'll have someone give you call today - I'll do it myself if nobody
else is available.

Alberto
